algorithm: The new algorithm calculates the scores for each bin based on the logarithm of the item size multiplied by the logarithm of the inverse of the rest capacities of the bins, to minimize the number of used bins.
code:
import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    log_item = np.log(item)
    log_inv_rest_cap = np.log(1 / bins)
    scores = log_item * log_inv_rest_cap
    return scores
